Violet, Countess of Grantham, played by Dame Maggie Smith in ITV drama, will be seen as her far younger self, with events taking place decades before the first series of Downton Abbey .
The Gilded Age will be set among the high society families of New York in the late 19th Century .
It will focus on the robber barons and get-rich-quick industrialists such as Cornelius Vanderbilt, John Jacob Astor and John D. Rockefeller .